<p>Chinese Recovery On Paper</p>
<p style="color: #000000;">Is China really growing at the reported 7.5% rate? I have frequently stated &#8220;no chance&#8221;. Malinvestments in housing, vacant cities, vacant malls, and roads with no traffic prove the point. Michael Pettis at China Financial Markets reiterates that view in [...]</p>
